kid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brazil_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We played great today, just like our first round,\\\" said Watson.\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2859, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2852, \"end\": 2858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Watson_(computer)\", \"score\": 0.9673193373565866, \"rank\": 0.03378475688821829, \"text\": \"Watson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Watson_(computer)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Watson_(computer)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We kept the same energy, the same positivity and the same mindset in wanting to enjoy it.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2951, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course we are focused and we are giving 1,000 per cent but we also wanted to smile through it.\", \"from\": 2952, \"to\": 3049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been dreaming since we got here.\", \"from\": 3051, \"to\": 3091, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The GB podium outfit is so cute.\", \"from\": 3092, \"to\": 3124, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3096, \"end\": 3098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9398019779427939, \"rank\": 0.06405380047473465, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So we are like, 'We have got to wear this'.\\\"\", \"from\": 3125, \"to\": 3169, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Andy Murray may be clinging on but it was the end of the road for another retiring three-time grand slam champion, with Angelique Kerber suffering a heartbreaking 6-7 (4) 6-4 7-6 (6) loss to China's Zheng Qinwen in the quarter-finals of the women's singles.\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3171, \"end\": 3182, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"s